\/li>\n<li>Demonstrated leadership ability (e.g., as shown through participation in community service, extracurricular, or other activities).<\/li>\n<li>Exceptional person success skill (emotional maturity, motivation, perseverance, etc.)<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2 id=\"required-documents-to-be-submitted\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"_Required_Documents_to_be_submitted\"><\/span>\u00a0<a name=\"_Toc80286123\"><\/a>Required Documents to be submitted<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li>A copy of his\/her most recent transcript (s) (submitted by the counselor)<\/li>\n<li>Student Aid Report (SAR), once the FAFSA has been completed<\/li>\n<li>Financial Aid Award Letter<\/li>\n<li>Letter of admission to a four-year bachelor\u2019s degree program at a non-profit, private, or public university.<\/li>\n<li>Headshot photo.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><strong>For more information visit<span style=\"color: #008000;\"> <a style=\"color: #008000;\" href=\"https:\/\/www.thegatesscholarship.org\/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">here.<\/a><\/span><\/strong><\/p>\n<p>See also&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;<a title=\"Apply Now | Canadian Institute of Technology Scholarship\" href=\"https:\/\/www.applyjobs.org.ng\/canadian-institute-of-technology-scholarship\/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Apply Now | Canadian Institute of Technology Scholarship <\/a><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"Gates Scholarship 2024\u2013Online Application for Graduate, Application login, Gates Scholars Application, Deadlines, Program requirements, and academic qualifications released&hellip;\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":1422,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[448],"tags":[657],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1420"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-jso